channel.title: Webclient loading problem
channel.description:
Hi all,
I uploaded all of my stuff on to the website and it loads, but it then goes to a white screen and says this:
"The requested URL /error_game_invalidhost.ws was not found on this server.
Additionally, a 404 Not Found error was encountered while trying to use an ErrorDocument to handle the request."
Any help would be appreciated. Thanks
